---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Editorial Policy | Senkai World"
  description="Learn about the editorial standards and publishing principles followed by Senkai World."
>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">
  <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">
    Editorial Policy
  </h1>

  <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-slate-400">
    Last Updated: July 2026
  </p>

  <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none prose-headings:text-white prose-p:text-slate-300 prose-li:text-slate-300">

    <p>
      At <strong>Senkai World</strong>, our goal is to provide accurate,
      engaging, and trustworthy content for anime and manhwa fans around the
      world. We are committed to maintaining high editorial standards across
      every article we publish.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Content</h2>

    <p>We publish content related to:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Anime News</li>
      <li>Manhwa News</li>
      <li>Anime Reviews</li>
      <li>Manhwa Recommendations</li>
      <li>Rankings and Lists</li>
      <li>Release Updates</li>
      <li>Guides and Features</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Our content is created to inform, entertain and help readers discover
      great series.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy</h2>

    <p>
      We strive to ensure that all information is accurate at the time of
      publication. Whenever possible, our news articles are based on official
      announcements, while reviews and rankings represent our editorial
      opinions.
    </p>

    <p>
      If new information becomes available, we update our content to keep it
      accurate and relevant.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>

    <p>
      Our recommendations and opinions are created independently. Advertisers
      or third parties do not influence our editorial decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>Corrections</h2>

    <p>
      If you notice factual errors or outdated information, please contact us
      at:
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>senkaiworld.in@gmail.com</strong>
    </p>

    <p>
      We review all correction requests and update articles whenever necessary.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>
      For editorial questions or feedback, contact us at:
    </p>

    <p>
      <strong>senkaiworld.in@gmail.com</strong>
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>